public record Game(String rawPgn, List<String> sanStrings, String annotator, String termination, String timeControl, String opening, String eco, String blackElo, String whiteElo, String result, String black, String white, String round, String date, String site, String event) extends Record
A record representing a game of chess. This is meant to be created with PgnParser.parse(String).

All fields of this class are a String, with the sole exception of sanStrings, which is a List<String>.

To parse sanStrings, one should use SanParser.parse(String, Position).
